data.description: Assumable VA loan at 2.25%! Experience the perfect blend of historic charm and modern luxury in the prestigious Lair Hill/South Portland Historic District. Elegance greets you at the door with a grand foyer entrance, setting the tone for a home that flows beautifully from one space to the next. This meticulously restored Victorian showcases high ceilings, new wood Marvin windows, a chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and balconies with incredible views. Its versatile layout can function as a grand single-family home with an additional kitchen, a duplex, multi-family living, or a short-term rental opportunity. The home is updated with two tankless water heaters and electrical systems, including separate breakers and meters. The primary suite boasts a spacious walk-in closet with an island and adjacent laundry for convenience. Additionally, built-in shelves throughout the home offer sophisticated storage solutions and display spaces. Outside, the living areas seamlessly merge, featuring a spiraling staircase that elegantly connects the balconies, covered patio, and a courtyard adorned with a newly built pergola, perfect for year round outdoor living. All in a central location with access to OHSU, John's Landing, downtown, bus lines, and bike lanes. [Home Energy Score = 1. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10011414]
